nodes.text: Minlan Weil and the Tam-honil Three

Minlan Weil and the Tam-honil Three were a band who operated following the Battle of Endor in 5 ABY. The band was led by Minlan Weil. Their music was played at Maz Kanata's castle when the Imperial Security Bureau Agent Romwell Krass Junior assaulted a New Republic pilot in revenge for the death of his family.
